         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Tuesday ¶ Dated to 8 May 1877 as theletter was registered in the Chief Secretary's Department on 11 May 1877, and the Tuesday before was the 8th. On 10 May, W. Odgers, Under Secretary, minuted: 'The C...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">77.05.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Odgers</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">L77/5633, unit 945, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Tuesday<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dated to 8 May 1877 as the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter was registered in the Chief Secretary's Department on 11 May 1877, and the Tuesday before was the 8th. On 10 May, W. Odgers, Under Secretary, minuted: 'The Chief Secretary informs me that he has seen the Gov. Botanist who waited upon him at his home this morning'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I should be grateful, dear Mr Odgers, to have a consultation with Mr M'Pherson,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. John MacPherson.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>more particularly as I feel not well. It would be most pleasing to me, if the hon. Gentleman would grant me a quiet evening hour early at his own residence, where I have been occasionally a guest.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
